58 bool DTTM::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
59 {
60 
61  U16 shifterU16;
62 
63  if (preservePos)
64  stream->push();
65 
66  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
67  mint = shifterU16;
68  shifterU16 >>= 6;
69  hr = shifterU16;
70  shifterU16 >>= 5;
71  dom = shifterU16;
72  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
73  mon = shifterU16;
74  shifterU16 >>= 4;
75  yr = shifterU16;
76  shifterU16 >>= 9;
77  wdy = shifterU16;
78 
79  if (preservePos)
80  stream->pop();
81  return true;
82 }

793 bool TC::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
794 {
795 
796  U16 shifterU16;
797 
798  if (preservePos)
799  stream->push();
800 
801  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
802  fFirstMerged = shifterU16;
803  shifterU16 >>= 1;
804  fMerged = shifterU16;
805  shifterU16 >>= 1;
806  fUnused = shifterU16;
807  brcTop.read(stream, false);
808  brcLeft.read(stream, false);
809  brcBottom.read(stream, false);
810  brcRight.read(stream, false);
811 
812  if (preservePos)
813  stream->pop();
814  return true;
815 }

828  fUnused = shifterU16;
829  brcTop.readPtr(ptr);
830  ptr += BRC::sizeOf;
831  brcLeft.readPtr(ptr);
832  ptr += BRC::sizeOf;
833  brcBottom.readPtr(ptr);
834  ptr += BRC::sizeOf;
835  brcRight.readPtr(ptr);
836  ptr += BRC::sizeOf;
837 }

1324 bool TAP::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
1325 {
1326 
1327  U16 shifterU16;
1328 
1329  if (preservePos)
1330  stream->push();
1331 
1332  jc = stream->readU16();
1333  dxaGapHalf = stream->readU16();
1334  dyaRowHeight = stream->readU16();
1335  fCantSplit = stream->readU8();
1336  fTableHeader = stream->readU8();
1337  tlp.read(stream, false);
1338  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
1339  fCaFull = shifterU16;
1340  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1341  fFirstRow = shifterU16;
1342  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1343  fLastRow = shifterU16;
1344  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1345  fOutline = shifterU16;
1346  shifterU16 >>= 1;
1347  unused12_4 = shifterU16;
1348  itcMac = stream->readU16();
1349  dxaAdjust = stream->readU16();
1350  rgdxaCenter = new U16[itcMac + 1];
1351  for (int _i = 0; _i < (itcMac + 1); ++_i)
1352  rgdxaCenter[_i] = stream->readU16();
1353  rgtc = new TC[itcMac];
1354  for (int _i = 0; _i < (itcMac); ++_i)
1355  rgtc[_i].read(stream, false);
1356  rgshd = new SHD[itcMac];
1357  for (int _i = 0; _i < (itcMac); ++_i)
1358  rgshd[_i].read(stream, false);
1359  for (int _i = 0; _i < (6); ++_i)
1360  rgbrcTable[_i].read(stream, false);
1361 
1362  if (preservePos)
1363  stream->pop();
1364  return true;
1365 }

1452 
1453 bool operator==(const TAP &lhs, const TAP &rhs)
1454 {
1455 
1456  if ((lhs.itcMac) != (rhs.itcMac))
1457  return false;
1458  for (int _i = 0; _i < (lhs.itcMac); ++_i) {
1459  if (lhs.rgdxaCenter[_i] != rhs.rgdxaCenter[_i])
1460  return false;
1461  }
1462 
1463  if ((lhs.itcMac) != (rhs.itcMac))
1464  return false;
1465  for (int _i = 0; _i < (lhs.itcMac); ++_i) {
1466  if (lhs.rgtc[_i] != rhs.rgtc[_i])
1467  return false;
1468  }
1469 
1470  if ((lhs.itcMac) != (rhs.itcMac))
1471  return false;
1472  for (int _i = 0; _i < (lhs.itcMac); ++_i) {
1473  if (lhs.rgshd[_i] != rhs.rgshd[_i])
1474  return false;
1475  }
1476 
1477  for (int _i = 0; _i < (6); ++_i) {
1478  if (lhs.rgbrcTable[_i] != rhs.rgbrcTable[_i])
1479  return false;
1480  }
1481 
1482  return lhs.jc == rhs.jc &&

4717 bool PAP::read(AbstractOLEStreamReader *stream, bool preservePos)
4718 {
4719 
4720  U8 shifterU8;
4721  U16 shifterU16;
4722 
4723  if (preservePos)
4724  stream->push();
4725 
4726  istd = stream->readU16();
4727  jc = stream->readU8();
4728  fKeep = stream->readU8();
4729  fKeepFollow = stream->readU8();
4730  fPageBreakBefore = stream->readU8();
4731  shifterU8 = stream->readU8();
4732  fBrLnAbove = shifterU8;
4733  shifterU8 >>= 1;
4734  fBrLnBelow = shifterU8;
4735  shifterU8 >>= 1;
4736  fUnused = shifterU8;
4737  shifterU8 >>= 2;
4738  pcVert = shifterU8;
4739  shifterU8 >>= 2;
4740  pcHorz = shifterU8;
4741  brcp = stream->readU8();
4742  brcl = stream->readU8();
4743  unused9 = stream->readU8();
4744  nLvlAnm = stream->readU8();
4745  fNoLnn = stream->readU8();
4746  fSideBySide = stream->readU8();
4747  dxaRight = stream->readS16();
4748  dxaLeft = stream->readS16();
4749  dxaLeft1 = stream->readS16();
4750  lspd.read(stream, false);
4751  dyaBefore = stream->readU16();
4752  dyaAfter = stream->readU16();
4753  phe.read(stream, false);
4754  fAutoHyph = stream->readU8();
4755  fWidowControl = stream->readU8();
4756  fInTable = stream->readU8();
4757  fTtp = stream->readU8();
4758  ptap = stream->readU16();
4759  dxaAbs = stream->readS16();
4760  dyaAbs = stream->readS16();
4761  dxaWidth = stream->readU16();
4762  brcTop.read(stream, false);
4763  brcLeft.read(stream, false);
4764  brcBottom.read(stream, false);
4765  brcRight.read(stream, false);
4766  brcBetween.read(stream, false);
4767  brcBar.read(stream, false);
4768  dxaFromText = stream->readU16();
4769  dyaFromText = stream->readU16();
4770  wr = stream->readU8();
4771  fLocked = stream->readU8();
4772  shifterU16 = stream->readU16();
4773  dyaHeight = shifterU16;
4774  shifterU16 >>= 15;
4775  fMinHeight = shifterU16;
4776  shd.read(stream, false);
4777  dcs.read(stream, false);
4778  anld.read(stream, false);
4779  itbdMac = stream->readU16();
4780  rgdxaTab = new U16[itbdMac];
4781  for (int _i = 0; _i < (itbdMac); ++_i)
4782  rgdxaTab[_i] = stream->readU16();
4783  rgtbd = new U8[itbdMac];
4784  for (int _i = 0; _i < (itbdMac); ++_i)
4785  rgtbd[_i] = stream->readU8();
4786 
4787  if (preservePos)
4788  stream->pop();
4789  return true;
4790 }
